Package com.soa.process.validation

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ActivityValidator
    An interface for performing activity specific validation.
    ValidationContext
    Provides context to an ActivityValidator, such as the activity definition to validate and access to a validation report in which errors and warnings can be stated.
